        "Id": "ce271430-1f21-4b95-a979-135afe9470f5",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Retrieving James (1)",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COLOMBIA",
        "PublicId": "112229352234",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/colombia/scene_hippo.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 11f4c01b-6c09-464a-b679-80923043fa20).Image",
        "Description": "It seems one &quot;James&quot; has gone missing on a family vacation to Colombia, where he and his family are to meet with his uncle, who lives there. Unfortunately, James got into some of the local nose candy and our client, Jack, wants him returned. Unfortunately, he learned of the hit and started running, so we need to kill a few of his contacts to get information. Kill his dealer, his uncle, and his mom in the village of Santa Fortuna. Good luck.",
